•	Manage the official group of the agency on the Russian social media channel Vk: generating a content plan; writing posts; creating flyers, banners, and other visuals (Adobe Photoshop); taking pictures; managing online marketing activities; creating and advertising promotional campaigns and giveaways.

•	Content generation and PR for bravegeeks.team:
   - author of the UX/UI Case Study: Redesigning a Public Transportation App for a Large Touristic City. Outcome: 2.2k claps, 6092 reads, 12915 views, 361 fans, and 1 lead within the first 10 days after its publication;
